{"tid":675659,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩賊劫海港城太子珠寶鐘錶 撬飾櫃玻璃掠千萬元首飾","createTime":"2018-05-23T17:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T17:22:06.000Z","uid":132750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f66693b8eeec652b13c309a193cb080ee0753f","tid":675659,"uid":132750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"兩賊匪劫尖沙咀珠寶行，撬飾櫃玻璃掠千萬元首飾！晚上7時許，2名戴口罩男子，闖入海港城3樓太子珠寶鐘錶行，一人以廣東話向職員叫了一聲「咪郁」，隨即用硬物撬開近門口的飾櫃玻璃，掠走5、6件首飾，歷時僅約一分鐘。賊匪得手後，立刻奪門而去，沿珠寶行對開的扶手電梯向地下逃去。珠寶行職員報警，警方接報盾牌趕至現場，封閉扶手電梯調查。警方翻看商場及珠寶行「天眼」追蹤賊匪去向，並在附近一帶搜捕匪蹤。 <br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查相信其中一名賊匪是本地人，另一人因無開口說話，暫未知其是本地、抑或內地人。油尖警區重案組跟進案件。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/mobile/bkn-20180523195410340-0523_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180523%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180523195410340-0523_00822_001.html&d=3Ib%2FLvzjMPqzHUsSTPQIODACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=ccae9af9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/mobile/bkn-20180523195410340-0523_00822_001.html</a><br />\n <br />\n都已經數唔到今年第幾單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c86545a4a8f4346610c115967ca34c706b60493","tid":675659,"uid":132750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/photo/bkn-20180523195410340-0523_00822_001_13p.jpg?20180524010523\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180523%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180523195410340-0523_00822_001_13p.jpg%3F20180524010523&h=4b1a1ff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快點拘捕我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/photo/bkn-20180523195410340-0523_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180523231603\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20